# _Pig Dice Game_

#### By Onesmus Mutungu

## Description

_This web application allows two players to play a game of Pig Dice._


 Player 1 inputs name and Player 2 inputs name, and click start button . Player 1:(name) Player 2:(name) then Click START  Goes to game console
Player 1 clicks ROLL button  and Dice rolls and number is generated
 If Player 1 rolls any number other than 1, that roll is added to round total  Roll = 2
 If Player 1 rolls a 1, no score is added and round for Player 1 ends  Roll = 1  Round total = 2 / Total score = 2 / Player 2 begins
 Repeat for Player 2  Roll = 1  Round total = 0  Total score = 0  Player 1 begins
 When a player's total score reaches 100 or more, game ends and winner page shows Player 1 total score = 100 Winner page


## Setup/Installation Requirements

* _git repository_
* _Open a HTML file_
* _chrome web browser or Firefox



## Technologies Used

* _HTML_
* _CSS_
* _Bootstrap_
* _JavaScript_
* _jQuery_
* _Atom


